description:
This is a 9 minute workout called 'Buteyko Breathing - Breathe Light, Slow & Deep | Guided Exercise for Anxiety & Brain Fog' from the channel The Buteyko Method.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises and Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

This is a guided Buteyko breathing exercise in which we will be breathing Light, Slow and Deep (Diaphragmatic Breathing).    It is also known as Breathe Light - Cadence Breathing.

This is a science backed breathing exercise, which when practiced regularly, can reduce symptoms of anxiety, brainfog, long covid and a whole host of chronic health conditions.
